    "The model by Nguyen-Vo et al.",
    "was trained with public datasets and used the DILIrank dataset as an independent set, which was the same test set that was used in this study.",
    "The performance of the models with hold-out validation and stratified k-fold cross validation is shown in Additional file 1: Tables S2 and S3.",
    "Additionally, the AUROC and AUPR performances are illustrated in Fig. 4 The performance calculated with hold-out validations are illustrated in Fig.",
    "In hold-out validation, accuracy varied from 0.81 to 0.90, sensitivity varied from 0.77 to 0.96, specificity varied from 0.62 to 0.90, precision Fig. 3 The overall experimental procedure."
